as [Selenium Manager](https://www.selenium.dev/blog/2022/introducing-selenium-manager/) which is now fully integrated with _Selenium_ will download the matching [GeckoDriver](https://stackoverflow.com/a/45510453/7429447) silently in the background and execute the test. 

